Collect essential details:

Destination(s)
Dates or trip length
Number of travellers and type of people joining (Mobility issues, disabilities, etc.)
Budget style (affordable, mid-range, luxury)
Interests (food, culture, nature, etc.)
Preferred pace (relaxed, balanced, fast)
Key constraints (mobility, weather, diet)
Miscellaneous (Visa, Passport)
Normalize details (e.g., dates, seasons) and store them in a simple JSON internally.
